<div class="right">
<h2 class="title">Rahul Siddharthan</h2>


<p><img alt="IMSc" src="imsc.jpg"
style="display: block; text-align: center; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto"
width="838" height="197"></p>
<a name="welcome"></a>
<div class="card">
<h3>Welcome</h3>
<P>
Welcome.  I am a member of the <A HREF="https://www.imsc.res.in/biology_imsc">computational biology group</A> at <A HREF="https://www.imsc.res.in/">Institute of Mathematical Sciences</A>, Chennai, India.

<P>
Main interests: Regulatory genomics, chromatin, chromosomes, centromeres, evolution, next-gen sequencing, etc.

<P>
My <A HREF="https://scholar.google.co.in/citations?hl=en&user=qBTnqj0AAAAJ&view_op=list_works&sortby=pubdate">publications/e-prints</A> (via Google Scholar)
</div>
<a name="software"></a>
<div class="card">
<H3>Software:</H3>
<B>NEW</B> <A HREF="./thicweed">THiCweed</A>: fast motif-finding in ChIP-seq data by clustering peaks<P>
<A HREF="./sigma2/">Sigma2</A>: aligning non-coding DNA<P>
<A HREF="./phylogibbs/">PhyloGibbs</A> and <A HREF="./phylogibbs-mp/">PhyloGibbs-MP</A>: ab-initio Gibbs-sampling motif-finders that take account of phylogeny
</div>
<a name="meetings"></a>
<div class="card">
<H3>Meetings</H3>
I have organised or co-organised a few mini-meetings over the years at IMSc, listed below:
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.imsc.res.in/~rsidd/aogcr2018">Aspects of gene and cellular regulation, 2018</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.imsc.res.in/~rsidd/biocs2016">Mini-meeting on the computer science/biology interface, 2016</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.imsc.res.in/~rsidd/aogcr2016">Aspects of gene and cellular regulation, 2016</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.imsc.res.in/~rsidd/aogr">Aspects of gene regulation, 2014</A>
</UL>
</div>
